=============
- papers/: 9 PDFs with README
- datasets/: README with download instructions, sample data
- code/: 2 cloned repos (awesome-story-generation, doc-storygen-v2)
- literature_review.md: Comprehensive synthesis
- resources.md: Complete catalog with recommendations

